et/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Embassy-830x830.png 830w, https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Embassy-230x230.png 230w, https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Embassy-350x350.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Literally built on Texas cuteness, we’re open annually during the week following Art Basel Miami Beach. Serving Sunday brunch 10 – 3.</em></figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2455\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Equinox.jpg\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-2455\" src=\"https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Equinox-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"“If I don’t make my 6:00 Soulcycle, who will I take to the saloon?&quot;\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Equinox-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Equinox-150x150.jpg 150w, https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Equinox-300x300.jpg 300w, https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Equinox-830x830.jpg 830w, https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Equinox-230x230.jpg 230w, https://d2rpbtor0vesnk.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marfa_Equinox-350x350.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>If I don’t make my 6:00 Soulcycle, who will I take to the saloon?</em></figcaption></figure>\n"},"meta":{"contributors":[{"title":{"rendered":"Wes Hiatt"},"slug":"wes-hiatt","meta":{"degree":"M.Arch I","graduation_year":"2017"}},{"title":{"rendered":"Ryan Connolly"},"slug":"ryan-connolly","meta"